        "path": "README.md",
        "exists": true,
        "size": 11331,
        "modified": "2026-04-01T02:27:10.178Z",
        "summary": "Primary project overview",
        "excerpt": "# Agentic Security System\n\nLangGraph-orchestrated host monitoring and deception pipeline for process, file, and network telemetry.\n\nThis project combines:\n- live telemetry collection\n- rule-based detection\n- ML routing and risk aggregation\n- LLM-based attacker analysis\n- LLM-based deception strategy planning\n- decoy deployment and file-response interception\n\nThe current runtime is centered around [main.py](/E:/agentic_ai/defense system/main.py), [agents/system_agent.py](/E:/agentic_ai/defense system/agents/system_agent.py), and [langgraph_pipeline.py](/E:/agentic_ai/defense system/langgraph_pipeline.py).\n\n![Workflow Diagram](/E:/agentic_ai/defense system/visual_flows.svg)\n\n## Overview\n"
      },
      {
        "path": "project.md",
        "exists": true,
        "size": 4498,
        "modified": "2026-06-09T05:46:28.820Z",
        "summary": "Project master guide",
        "excerpt": "# Project Master Guide\n\nThis repository is an agentic security and deception system that monitors process, file, and network telemetry, scores suspicious behavior, routes suspicious events into ML models, asks an LLM to infer attacker intent and stage, and then deploys decoys plus interception rules for controlled real or fake file responses. Sources: [README.md#L3](/E:/agentic_ai/defense system/README.md#L3), [langgraph_pipeline.py#L25](/E:/agentic_ai/defense system/langgraph_pipeline.py#L25), [core/interception_layer.py#L90](/E:/agentic_ai/defense system/core/interception_layer.py#L90).\n\n## What To Read First\n\n1. [PROJECT_UNDERSTANDING.md](/E:/agentic_ai/defense system/PROJECT_UNDERSTANDING.md)\n2. [BUG_AUDIT.md](/E:/agentic_ai/defense system/BUG_AUDIT.md)\n3. [SECURITY_REVIEW.md](/E:/agentic_ai/defense system/SECURITY_REVIEW.md)\n4. [PRODUCTION_READINESS_REPORT.md](/E:/agentic_ai/defense system/PRODUCTION_READINESS_REPORT.md)\n5. [UI_UX_DESIGN.md](/E:/agentic_ai/defense system/UI_UX_DESIGN.md)\n6. [DASHBOARD_IMPLEMENTATION_PLAN.md](/E:/agentic_ai/defense system/DASHBOARD_IMPLEMENTATION_PLAN.md)\n\n## Fast Mental Model\n\n- Entry point: [main.py#L64](/E:/agentic_ai/defense system/main.py#L64)\n- Runtime loop: [agents/system_agent.py#L19](/E:/agentic_ai/defense system/agents/system_agent.py#L19)\n- Workflow graph: [langgraph_pipeline.py#L58](/E:/agentic_ai/defense system/langgraph_pipeline.py#L58)"
      },
