        "summary": "Architecture understanding",
        "excerpt": "# Project Understanding\n\nThis document is based on recursive inspection of the repository in `E:\\agentic_ai\\defense system`. It focuses on the active runtime, which the repository itself centers around `main.py`, `agents/system_agent.py`, and `langgraph_pipeline.py`, while the `src/` tree is largely placeholder legacy scaffolding. Sources: [README.md#L3](/E:/agentic_ai/defense system/README.md#L3), [README.md#L34](/E:/agentic_ai/defense system/README.md#L34), [main.py#L64](/E:/agentic_ai/defense system/main.py#L64), [agents/system_agent.py#L6](/E:/agentic_ai/defense system/agents/system_agent.py#L6), [langgraph_pipeline.py#L25](/E:/agentic_ai/defense system/langgraph_pipeline.py#L25), [src/inference/pipeline.py#L11](/E:/agentic_ai/defense system/src/inference/pipeline.py#L11).\n\n## Architecture Diagram\n\n```mermaid\nflowchart LR\n    A[\"main.py\"] --> B[\"SystemAgent.start()\"]\n    B --> C[\"LangGraphSecurityPipeline\"]\n    C --> D[\"Monitor.collect()\"]\n    D --> D1[\"ProcessCollector\"]\n    D --> D2[\"FileCollector\"]\n    D --> D3[\"NetworkCollector\"]\n    C --> E[\"EventEnricher\"]\n    C --> F[\"EventFilter\"]\n    C --> G[\"ScoringDetector\"]\n    C --> H[\"SOCLogger\"]"
